REMARK 400                                                                      
REMARK 400 COMPOUND                                                             
REMARK 400 THE CONFORMATIONS OF THE TWO MONOMERS ARE DIFFERENT AS THE           
REMARK 400 RESULT OF A DIFFERENCE IN CONFORMATION AT THE N-TERMINI              
